title: Google\Cloud\ArtifactRegistry\V1beta2\ListFilesRequest
name: ListFilesRequest
description:
The request to list files.

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.parent
params.description: The name of the repository whose files will be listed. For example: "projects/p1/locations/us-central1/repositories/repo1

params.name: data.filter
params.description: An expression for filtering the results of the request. Filter rules are case insensitive. The fields eligible for filtering are: name owner An example of using a filter: name="projects/p1/locations/us-central1/repositories/repo1/files/a/b/*" --> Files with an ID starting with "a/b/". owner="projects/p1/locations/us-central1/repositories/repo1/packages/pkg1/versions/1.0" --> Files owned by the version 1.0 in package pkg1.

params.name: data.page_size
params.description: The maximum number of files to return.

params.name: data.page_token
params.description: The next_page_token value returned from a previous list request, if any.
